snippet.title: Blockbuster Inc Release Date Trailer - Future Games Show Spring Showcase 2024
snippet.description:
Super Sly Fox shared a gameplay trailer for Blockbuster Inc., the movie studio simulation game in which you build lots, develop talent, and take on Hollywood. It’s coming to PC on June 6, 2024. 

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#FutureGamesShow #FGS #blockbusterinc #blockbusterincgame
